"既に公開されている静的ファイルを返すミドルウェアは古いものが多かったので筆者の方で用意しました。"
msgstr "Let&#39;s activate middleware that distributes static files only in the development environment. Implementation of static file delivery method is omitted here. Middleware that returns already published static files was old, so many of them were prepared, so I prepared it by the author."

